        <p style="font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #676F7C; ">Founded in 2021 with a single salvage yard in ISTANBUL, H&A has grown into a global auto auction company. Since 2021 H&A TURKEY has been remarketing salvage vehicles of fleet managers and insurance companies through online car auctions for national and international dealers, dismantlers and body shops. We currently operate in&nbsp;more than 200 locations in 11 countries.</p>
