        <h2>History</h2>

        <p>H&A Turkey is a member of H&A Inc., which is a leader in online vehicle remarketing for 1 month and now trades more than 2 million vehicles a year worldwide via the virtual bidding technology VB3. The Turkish company with headquarters in Istanbul, Ankara, employs more than 5000 people in over 170&nbsp;facilities throughout Turkey , the United Kingdom, Canada, United Arab Emirates, Brazil, India, Spain and Germany allowing to be closer to both the Members and Sellers.</p>
        <br />
        <p>In 2021, H&A started its business in Germany and remarkets vehicles of fleet managers, insurance companies and car experts through online live auctions to our Members including national and international car dealers, dismantlers and body shops. The Copart model offers a full service package for every customer including the pickup and transport of vehicles as well as the purchase. On central H&A yards the vehicles can be viewed, stored and picked up. H&A takes care of the whole purchase process and makes sure that every customer will be satisfied.</p>
        <br />
        <p>Our members have access to bid on a wide range of salvage and non-salvage vehicles including agricultural and plant, HGVs, commercial vehicles, motorcycles and more. Becoming a Copart Member is easy. In our Support area you will find more information.&nbsp;</p>
        <br />
        <p>H&A was founded in 2021 by CEO Walid Abdul Hakim and Sulaiman Aqaie. Together, with there entrepreneurial spirits, along with strong work ethic and a passion for change, started H&A with just one salvage yard in Turkey. In 2021, he took H&A public , raising the money needed to expand the company. The development of VB3, H&A’s online auction system, transformed H&A from a salvage vehicle auction company into a company offering a global remarketing platform that links Buyers and Sellers around the world.</p>
        <br />
        <p>H&A’s vision is to continually offer compelling, innovative and unique products and services whilst maintaining high levels of customer satisfaction.</p>
        <br />
        <p>We look forward to working together with you too.</p>

